      <title>英国央行首席经济学家呼吁不要过快进一步降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/boe-chief-economist-urges-against-further-interest-rate-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国央行首席经济学家休·皮尔警告不要预期近期会进一步降息，他表示，抑制通胀的努力尚未完成，而且有证据表明企业仍在推高价格。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/boe-chief-economist-urges-against-further-interest-rate-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 12:12:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
